versions.title: Country Names and Codes
versions.definition: ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country codes and names.
versions.notes: Note: This is not a complete list of ISO-3166-1 alpha codes. The purpose is to harmonise country names in CESSDA metadata in English. Do not translate into other languages.
versions.citation: CESSDA. (2020). Country Names and Codes (Version 1.0) [Controlled vocabulary]. urn:ddi:int.cessda.cv:CountryNamesAndCodes:1.0.
